comment:
* PeriodicAdvertisingReport for Bluetooth LE synchronized advertising.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: DATA_INCOMPLETE_TRUNCATED
variables.comment:
* The data returned is incomplete. The controller was unsuccessful to receive all chained
     * packets, returning only partial data.

variables.name: mTimestampNanos
variables.comment: Device timestamp when the result was last seen.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
public int getTxPower()
methods.comment:
* Returns the transmit power in dBm. The valid range is [-127, 126]. Value of 127 means
     * information was not available.

methods.name: public int getRssi()
methods.comment: Returns the received signal strength in dBm. The valid range is [-127, 20].

methods.name: public int getDataStatus()
methods.comment:
* Returns the data status. Can be one of {@link PeriodicAdvertisingReport#DATA_COMPLETE} or
     * {@link PeriodicAdvertisingReport#DATA_INCOMPLETE_TRUNCATED}.

methods.name: public ScanRecord getData()
methods.comment: Returns the data contained in this periodic advertising report.

methods.name: public long getTimestampNanos()
methods.comment: Returns timestamp since boot when the scan record was observed.

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
